    "(3) Self-repair testThe next stage in post-build acceptance and integration coding is functional and non-functional testing.",
    "Here, the use of AI and machine learning for code creation as well as self-healing test code and maintenance has become a reality in the DevOps space.",
    "Test automation can be a huge bottleneck and is often the cause of project delays.",
    "Unreliable automation can affect the testing process.",
    "One of the root causes of unreliable test automation is the constant change of the application under test and the elements used in the test."
